protected_spaces_details.description: Provision for children and young people

description: Demolition of all existing buildings, and construction of seven new buildings of between 1-storey and 18-storeys, containing 374 residential units; non-residential institution (D1) floorspace; business (B1) floorspace; flexible retail/restaurant & cafe/business (A1/A3/B1) floorspace; flexible residential/business (C3/B1) floorspace; flexible non-residential institution/business floorspace (D1/B1); and an electricity sub-station.   The proposals include a basement, vehicle/cycle parking, plant, the alteration of the vehicle access from Thessaly Road, and associated works and landscaping. (Please note that the on-site ball court would be removed as part of the proposals). An Environmental Statement has been submitted with the application under the Town and Country Planning (Environmental Impact Assessment) Regulations 2011.
